               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18511027-name-107" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-107" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-107" type="surname" value="MORBEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-107" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES MORBEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep the Sun public-house, Long Acre. On 8th Oct. the prisoner came for a glass of gin—it came to 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he drank it, and put down a shilling—I saw it was bad, and asked him if he had any more money about him—he said, no, he could not pay for the gin unless I took the shilling—a policeman came in, and I gave him the shilling.</p>
               <p>
